=== VM Native Function Integration Tests ===

Math Functions:
  abs(-42) = 42
  sqrt(144) = 12
  pow(2, 10) = 1024
  floor(3.9) = 3
  ceil(3.1) = 4
  round(3.7) = 4
  min(5, 10) = 5
  max(5, 10) = 10
  ✓ Math functions work

String Functions:
  len('hello') = 5
  to_upper('hello') = HELLO
  to_lower('WORLD') = world
  trim('  test  ') = test
  capitalize('hello') = Hello
  ✓ String functions work

Array Functions:
  Array: [1, 2, 3]
  len([1,2,3]) = 3
  push(arr, 4) = [1, 2, 3, 4]
  ✓ Array functions work

Type Conversions:
  to_int('123') = 123
  to_float('3.14') = 3.14
  to_string(456) = 456
  to_bool(1) = true
  ✓ Type conversion functions work

Range Function:
  range(5) = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
  range(3, 8) = [3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  ✓ Range function works

Dict Functions:
  Dict: {"a": 1, "b": 2}
  keys(dict) = [a, b]
  values(dict) = [1, 2]
  ✓ Dict functions work

Date/Time Functions:
  now() returns: float
  ✓ Date/time functions work

Random Functions:
  random() returns: float
  random_int(1, 100) returns: int
  ✓ Random functions work

=== All VM Native Function Tests Passed! ===

